            <!-- About company -->
            <div class="block">
              <h3 class="block-title sub-title">How It All Began</h3>
              <p>IFace Global is an initiative by the young minds with an aim to make an impact through smart solutioning by the help of IT and Embedded Technologies. We have realized that there is a huge gap between the IT Industry and the Embedded Components and planned to build high end smart solutions with an integration of IT and Embedded Components. Our focus areas are Agriculture, Animal Farming, Forest and Natural Resource Preservation, Education, eGovernnce etc. the domains that are neglected by today's fast growing Indian Technology companies.</p>
              
              <h3 class="block-title sub-title">Our Philosophy</h3>
              <p>Our vision is to make this world a smart and better place to live in by developing solutions that aim to make human life more comfortable and convenient. We believe there are many small problems and if these are addressed properly then the solutions can have huge impact on our life with a social as well as business potential.</p>
  
              <h3 class="block-title sub-title">What's In A Name?</h3>
              <p>The name IFace has been derived from the word InterFace, which is to integrate off the shelf components and develop solutions that caters to small but significant problems, solutions to which can have huge impact on the RoI of the companies as well as Government organizations.</p>
            </div>
            
